&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;


&lt;p&gt;以特定单位打印&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class="codehilite"&gt;&lt;pre&gt;&lt;span class="n"&gt;du&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="o"&gt;-&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="n"&gt;b&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="o"&gt;/-&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="n"&gt;k&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="o"&gt;/-&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="n"&gt;m&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="o"&gt;/-&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="n"&gt;B&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="n"&gt;FILES&lt;/span&gt;
